Name:
* Vikcoria Valyukevich RUS disqualified for an anti-doping rule violation according to IOC Disciplinary Commissions desicion of March 15 2017. 




Women's Triple jump - Athletics - London 2012 Summer Olympics
Event Format:
     
     Athletes competed in a qualifying round followed by the final. Top twelve and ties in the qualifying round and all those reaching the announced qualification limit advanced to the final. In the final all finalists were given three tries. The top eight were then given three more. Event facts: Women's Triple jump competition was held at the Olympic Stadium and 35 athletes participated in the event.
